3ï¸âƒ£ Token Automation (Strongly Recommended)

In Login requests, add this to Tests tab:

Factory Admin Login

pm.environment.set("adminToken", pm.response.json().token);
pm.environment.set("token", pm.response.json().token);

Dealer Login

pm.environment.set("dealerToken", pm.response.json().token);
pm.environment.set("token", pm.response.json().token);

Service Center Login

pm.environment.set("serviceToken", pm.response.json().token);
pm.environment.set("token", pm.response.json().token);


